info.author: L. C. Rees
info.description:
A collection of Python dictionary types that support attribute-style access.
Includes *defaultdict*,  *OrderedDict*, restricted, *ChainMap*, *Counter*, and
frozen implementations plus miscellaneous utilities for writing Python software.
info.keywords: dict attribute collection mapping dot notation access bunch
info.name: stuf
info.summary: Normal, default, ordered, chained, restricted, counter, and frozen dictionaries with attribute-style access.
